What's life like when you're married to a professional baseball player? During the season, when the team is at home, guys leave at 1PM and get home at 1AM; not exactly prime kid/family hours. When the team is on the road, it's for a couple weeks at a time in 3-4 cities. So what do you do? For Heather Zimmerman, the choice was simple: Pack the kids up and board the plane. What's it like dealing with angry fans on social media? How do you use your platform to help others? Did Heather like baseball before she met Ryan?&nbsp;


