Are Americans not taking care of themselves and potential medical issues because they are afraid of Covid-19? Why have melanoma cases gone up 47% over the last decade? How complicated is the relationship between pharmaceutical companies, doctors, and the needs of their patients? Dr. Terrence Keaney has a dermatology practice just outside of Washington, DC (https://www.skindcderm.com%29/ (https://www.skindcderm.com)) that combines a wide range of procedures, patient care, and research. He was terrific with us on the above topics, why men aren't as good as women at taking care of themselves, and his late-game switch that led him to being happy.&nbsp;


